HEADWORD: Cassinette
<hw>Cas`si*nette"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Sp.
<ets>casinete</ets>, G. <ets>cassinet</ets>.]</ety> <def>A cloth with a
